        "compareChart": {
            "value": "<mas-compare-chart expanded-groups=\"all\"><span slot=\"compare-features\">Compare Features</span><div name=\"adobe-apps\"> <h4>Adobe apps</h4> <p name=\"seamless-integration\"> Seamless integration across Adobe apps like Photoshop, Illustrator, InDesign, Firefly, Acrobat and Lightroom </p> <p name=\"boost-photoshop\" >Boost your creativity with Photoshop <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"In addition to the Adobe Express Premium plan, get full access to Adobe Photoshop on web and mobile.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"firefly-pro\" >Adobe Firefly Pro <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Create images, video, vector graphics. Ideate, create, and collaborate with Firefly Boards. Work with the latest commercially safe Firefly generative AI models.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"aem-workfront-genstudio\"> Integration with Adobe Experience Manager, Workfront, and GenStudio for performance marketing </p> </div><div name=\"template-and-design-assets\"> <h4>Template and design assets</h4> <p name=\"pro-templates\" >Professionally designed templates <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Static, motion, and video templates.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"template-recommendations\" >Template recommendations <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Preview your photo in fully editable templates that complement the context of your photo.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"stock-photos\">Adobe Stock photos</p> <p name=\"stock-videos\">Adobe Stock videos</p> <p name=\"stock-audio-music\">Adobe Stock audio/music</p> <p name=\"stock-sfx\">Adobe Stock sound effects</p> <p name=\"stock-backgrounds\">Adobe Stock backgrounds</p> <p name=\"stock-design-assets\" >Adobe Stock design assets <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Illustrations, brushes, textures, frames, and more.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"stock-icons\">Adobe Stock icons</p> <p name=\"basic-shapes\">Basic Shapes</p> </div><div name=\"generative-ai\"> <h4>Generative AI</h4> <p name=\"ai-assistant\">AI Assistant (Beta) <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Prompt-anything, edit-everything\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"generate-presentations\" >Generate Presentations <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Turn your documents into presentations in minutes\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"generative-credits\">Generative Credits</p> <p name=\"generate-content\"> Generate Images, text effects, templates and more </p> <p name=\"insert-remove-objects\">Insert and Remove Objects</p> <p name=\"commercial-use\" >Commercial Use <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Create content with features designed to be commercially safe, powered by Adobe Firefly generative AI.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"gen-5s-videos\">Generate 5-second videos</p> </div><div name=\"photo-and-design\"> <h4>Photo and design</h4> <p name=\"erase\">Erase</p> <p name=\"photo-adjustments\" >Photo Adjustments &amp; Effects <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Adjust contrast, shadows, saturation and more, or add effects and blend modes, powered by Photoshop\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"start-from-photos\" >Start from photos <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Start from a JPG, PNG, PSD, and more to bring your photo into the all-in-one editor.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"adobe-fonts\">Adobe Fonts</p> <p name=\"font-recommendations\" >Font recommendations <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"See recommendations for fonts that match the style of your design\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"sync-psd-ai\" >Add and sync your .psd and .ai files <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Add .psd or .ai files to your design. Edits made in Photoshop or Illustrator will sync so you don't need to reimport your assets\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"export-formats\">Export in JPEG, PNG, PDF, GIF, PPT</p> <p name=\"export-png-transparent\"> Export as PNG with transparent background </p> <p name=\"draw-paint\"> Draw and paint with 85+ brushes and coloring pages </p> </div><div name=\"video-and-motion\"> <h4>Video and motion</h4> <p name=\"drag-drop-video\">Drag-and-drop video creation</p> <p name=\"remove-video-bg\">Remove video background</p> <p name=\"animate-all\" >Animate All <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Automatically apply motion to your entire design\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"dynamic-animations\" >Dynamic Animations <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Add physics-based animation to your photos, videos, text, shapes, and icons.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"voiceover-record\"> Record voiceover and video directly in-app </p> <p name=\"video-transitions\">Video transitions</p> <p name=\"video-length\">Video length</p> <p name=\"export-4k\">Export in 4K</p> <p name=\"enhance-speech\">Enhance Speech</p> <p name=\"tiktok-symphony\" >TikTok Symphony Assistant Add-on <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"1M+ songs and sounds from TikTok's Commercial Music Library\">ℹ️</a></p> </div><div name=\"quick-actions\"> <h4>Quick Actions</h4> <p name=\"remove-img-bg\">Remove Image Background</p> <p name=\"resize-image\">Resize Image</p> <p name=\"crop-image\">Crop Image</p> <p name=\"qr-code\">Generate QR Code</p> <p name=\"pdf-quick-actions\"> PDF Quick Actions: Edit, Combine, Organize, Import/Enhance PDF </p> <p name=\"convert-gif\">Convert to GIF</p> <p name=\"convert-jpg-png-svg\">Convert to JPG/PNG/SVG</p> <p name=\"caption-video\">Caption Video</p> <p name=\"resize-video\">Resize Video</p> <p name=\"clip-maker\" >Clip Maker <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Turn video podcasts, educational videos, and product reviews into social clips with captions\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"merge-crop-trim-video\">Merge, Crop, and Trim Video</p> <p name=\"animate-characters\">Animate Characters</p> </div><div name=\"brand-management-and-collaboration\"> <h4>Brand management and collaboration</h4> <p name=\"brand-kits\" >Brand Kits <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Keep all your fonts, colors, logos and graphics in one brand kit.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"extract-brand-assets\"> Extract brand colors, fonts, logos from image in one-click </p> <p name=\"libraries\" >Libraries <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Store all your Adobe Express and Creative Cloud assets in one place.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"branded-templates\" >Branded templates <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Create brand-specific templates for use across all your teams.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"brand-controls\" >Brand controls <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Specify which brand colors and fonts can be used in a shared template and enforce with password-protected locked template elements.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"custom-home\" >Custom Home <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Featured branded banner and instant access to approved on-brand templates\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"aem-integration\" >Adobe Experience Manager integration <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Access and edit assets from Experience Manager and save back to your Experience Manager repository.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"custom-models\" >Custom Models <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Generate on-brand content with Firefly Custom Models.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"protect-your-brand\" >Protect your brand <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"IP indemnification for Adobe Firefly generated content\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"realtime-coediting\"> Real-time co-editing and commenting </p> <p name=\"share-templates\">Share templates across teams</p> </div><div name=\"campaigns-and-publishing\"> <h4>Campaigns and publishing</h4> <p name=\"resize\" >Resize <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Resize for multiple formats - at one time, in the same file\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"translate\" >Translate <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Automatically translate text into 45+ languages.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"safe-zones\" >Safe Zones <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Format-aware guides to keep important text, visuals, and logos visible\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"caption-writer\" >Caption Writer <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"AI-generated social captions tailored to your design\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"social-mentions\" >Social Mentions <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Add mentions directly in captions when scheduling posts\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"content-scheduler\" >Content Scheduler <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Plan, publish, and schedule direct to social channels\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"shared-calendars\">Shared social calendars</p> <p name=\"paid-ads\">Publish paid ads directly</p> <p name=\"multi-channel\"> Publish to multiple channels simultaneously </p> <p name=\"metricool\" >Metricool Add-On <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Track key social metrics, competitive insights, and download custom reports.\">ℹ️</a></p> </div><div name=\"support-and-storage\"> <h4>Support and storage</h4> <p name=\"cloud-storage\">Cloud storage</p> <p name=\"version-history\">Version history</p> <p name=\"admin-console\">Admin Console <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"License/user management.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"flexible-license-mgmt\" >Flexible license management <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Reassign licenses when there are changes to your team.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"admin-roles\" >Admin roles <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Assign total access to select staff.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"asset-reclamation\" >Asset reclamation <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Control of corporate assets and retrieve assets when users leave the org.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"consolidated-billing\">Consolidated billing</p> <p name=\"support-247\" >24x7 technical support <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Available in multiple languages from customer care team, dedicated line for admins.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"expert-sessions\" >1:1 sessions with product experts <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Accessible from Admin Console.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"sso\">Single sign-on</p> <p name=\"encryption-key\" >Encryption key support <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Assets can be encrypted for additional layer of security\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"user-directory-sync\" >User directory sync <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Automate Adobe user management process when synched with Microsoft Azure or Google Admin Console.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"firefly-indemnification\" >Firefly output indemnification <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"Select plans eligible for IP indemnification for Firefly generated images.\">ℹ️</a></p> <p name=\"flexible-purchasing\" >Flexible purchasing options <a href=\"#\" class=\"secondary-link\" title=\"For purchasing, deploying, and managing Adobe licenses according to an organization's business needs.\">ℹ️</a></p> </div></mas-compare-chart>",
